item.title: About
item.description: Hello! I decided to write a short introduction about me below. I plan on adding more in the future. About Me Hello World! My name is Xinpeng and I’m currently a high school student who’s interested in coding! I am currently developing minecraft plugins and other projects. I very much enjoy helping other people, and if you would like to contact me for some reason, DM my discord or any social media below.
